bilingual.source: They bought a cow to start their dairy farm.
bilingual.target: 他们买了一头奶牛来开始他们的奶牛场。

bilingual.source: The cow is eating grass in the field.
The cow provides milk for the entire family.
The cow is a common animal on the farm.
bilingual.target: 奶牛是农场里常见的动物。

bilingual.source: The farmer milks the cow every morning.
bilingual.target: 农夫每天早上挤奶牛的奶。

bilingual.source: The little boy likes to play with the cow.
bilingual.target: 小男孩喜欢和奶牛玩耍。

bilingual.source: The cow grazes peacefully in the meadow.
bilingual.target: 奶牛在草地上安静地吃草。

bilingual.source: This cow produces a lot of milk every day.
bilingual.target: 这头奶牛每天产很多牛奶。

bilingual.source: Bessie is the friendliest cow on the farm.
bilingual.target: 贝西是农场里最友好的奶牛。

bilingual.source: The farmer cleaned the cow's teat before milking.
bilingual.target: 农夫在挤奶前清洗了奶牛的乳头。

list.abstract: COW（kaʊ）英语单词，动词、名词，作动词的意思是“威胁，恐吓”，作名词的意思是“奶牛，母牛；母兽”。

yingyinNormal.en: Tiddles is climbing higher in the tree. Come here, you little pickle. Mummy Cow is climbing into the tree. Be careful, Mommy Cow.
yingyinNormal.zh: 小土豆爬到了更高的地方。快过来，绿色的小捣蛋。奶牛妈妈跟着爬到了树上。小心一点，奶牛妈妈。

yingyinNormal.en: The cow goes moo. The horse goes neigh. It's all the people talked back then.
yingyinNormal.zh: 奶牛哞哞叫，小马咴咴叫，那会儿人们就只会说这些。

yingyinNormal.en: Mrs. Cow is waiting for the train at the next station. What's happened to the big train? Has it shrunk? No, this is a toy train. Gertrude is not a toy. She's a miniature locomotive. Off we go.
yingyinNormal.zh: 奶牛夫人在下一个火车站等会火车。大火车怎么了？他是变小了吗？不是的，这是一辆玩具火车。格特鲁德号不是玩具火车，他不过是一辆微型火车而已。我们出发了！

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, yeah, you're right, Moni-cow. Okay, I hear you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 说得也是，莫母牛。我懂了。
他被扔进去了，我的天呐。

yingyinNormal.en: And he's standing next to this cow, and the cow says, "Elmoo."
yingyinNormal.zh: 阿母站在牛旁边，牛说了：阿母-母-母-母。

yingyinNormal.en: Hindus do the same thing. Except they leave room for a cow.
yingyinNormal.zh: 印度人也这样，只不过他们留空间给牛。

yingyinNormal.en: Let's face it. We're not going to run the country on cow power alone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们必须面对它，美国并不只靠生物气体来维持运转。

yingyinNormal.en: It's part of a larger program called cow power that serves more than 3,000 customers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是所谓的生物能的大工程的一部分，它能给3000多户家庭提供服务。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, come on. Childbirth is a natural, beautiful... Oh, it's like someone sawed a cow in half.
yingyinNormal.zh: 拜托，分娩是一个自然而又美丽的... 就像一头牛被人锯成了两半。

yingyinNormal.en: Vermont is the first state with a utility that's banking on cow power. But doesn't come cheap.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佛蒙特州是第一个依赖生物能发电的州，但这花费也不少。

yingyinNormal.en: Why can't you get back together with Leonard? I bet Leonard never tipped a cow over on himself.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你为什么就不能跟莱纳德和好呢？我敢说莱纳德从来不会惹祸上身。

yingyinNormal.en: Do not tell me about my own culture, Sheldon! In the mood I'm in, I'll take you out. I swear to cow!
yingyinNormal.zh: 不需要你教我自家的文化，谢尔顿。就我现在的心情，老子会揪你出去的。我向牛发誓。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, I accept that. When Janice asked me and I said no, she took that to mean that I was calling her a cow.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这点我可以接受，当珍妮丝问我时，我回答不，她却认为我说她像母牛。

yingyinNormal.en: The community stepped up and said we want to pay more for cow power, and it's become much bigger than we initially ever dreamed that it was gonna be.
yingyinNormal.zh: 社区已经增加的投资，并说道我们想增加对生物气体的投资，而且这比我们最初需要的高得多了它正在变高。

yingyinNormal.en: 45. 45 seconds is plenty of time for a woman to walk through that door and fall in love with me. You know, probably half that if I break out the old cow eyes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 45秒。45秒足够一个女人走进那扇门然后爱上我了，要是用上我这双明眸，时间还要减半呢。

examination_example.sentence: The lag time it takes to add more <highlight>cows</highlight> to a herd to meet demand can result in events like the recent cheese surplus.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 为满足需求而增加牛群所需的滞后时间可能导致发生最近类似的奶酪过剩事件。

examination_example.sentence: The price of grain they feed their <highlight>cows</highlight> has gone up, tightening their profit margins.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们喂养奶牛的谷物价格上涨，积压了他们的利润空间。

examination_example.sentence: I've reported that advances in livestock protection are happening with scientists painting eyes on the butts of <highlight>cows</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我曾报道说，随着科学家在牛屁股上画上眼睛，家畜保护正在取得进展。

examination_example.sentence: Researchers have been devising and testing a method of trickery to make lions think they are being watched by the painted eyes on <highlight>cow</highlight> butts.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 研究人员一直在设计和测试一种骗术，让狮子认为画在牛屁股上的眼睛在注视着它们。
